And we prescribe blood pressure cuffs, thermometers, and pulse socks.

00:03:12.960 --> 00:03:16.800
And we instruct them to take vital signs every six hours at home.

00:03:17.180 --> 00:03:22.300
We give them a wallet card and also instruct them to take Tylenol and dexamethasone formula.

