And we give them a wallet card and also instruct them to take Tylenol and dexamethasone formula.

00:03:22.520 --> 00:03:22.580
And we give them a wallet card and also instruct them to take Tylenol and dexamethasone formula.

00:03:22.580 --> 00:03:22.620
And we give them a wallet card and also instruct them to take Tylenol and dexamethasone formula.

